WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:02.440
Damn it! We have favourites in South Africa.

00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:04.440
The favourites in South Africa are the people

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:07.840
who are being repressed by that ugly white regime.

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:09.180
We have favourites.

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:11.200
Our loyalty is not the South Africa,

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.580
is the South Africans.

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:15.380
And the South Africans are majority black.

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:17.580
And they are being excoriated.

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:21.520
It is not to some stupid puppet government over there.

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:23.980
It is not to the Afrikaners regime.

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:26.140
We have no loyalty to them.

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:28.480
We have no loyalty to South Africa,

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:29.940
to South Africans.
